high_descs: move to the counter to the right of the sink
pick up a mug from the counter
move to the fridge behind you
chill the mug in the fridge for a moment
move to the coffee maker to the right of the stove
put the mug on the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled mug on the coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn right and walk through the kitchen to the counter just right of the sink
Pick up the white mug from the counter
Turn right and go to the fridge
Put the mug into the fridge then remove it
Turn around and walk over to the coffee maker right of the oven
Put the mug in the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled mug in the coffee maker

high_descs: Turn right and take a step then turn right and walk to the fridge then turn left and walk to the counter.
Pick up the mug that's in front of you.
Turn right and take a step right so you can use the fridge.
Chill the mug in the fridge then get it back out and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the stove then turn right and walk to the counter.
Put the mug under the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold mug under the coffee maker.

high_descs: Walk into the kitchen and up to the counter right of the sink
Pick up the white mug from the counter
Turn and walk to the fridge
Put the mug into the fridge and then remove it
Turn and walk to the coffee maker on the kitchen counter
Put the mug in the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled mug in the coffee maker

high_descs: Walk to the microwave and stand facing the sink.
Pick up the mug near the right side of the sink.
Turn around and move to the front of the fridge so you face it.
Chill the mug in the fridge before taking it back out.
Turn around and walk until you hit the stove then turn right and walk to the toaster.
Place the mug in it's spot on the coffee pot.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled mug under the coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn around, veer left and stop at the counter to the right of the sink.
Pick the mug up off of the counter.
Turn right and walk to the fridge.
Put the mug in the fridge and close it. Wait a moment a take the mug out of the fridge again.
Turn around and veer right to the corner of the counter top with the coffee maker in it.
Put the cup in the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup in the correct place of the single-cup coffee maker.
